        public static <D,N extends GraphUtils.TarjanNode<D>> List<? extends List<? extends N>> tarjan(java.lang.Iterable<? extends N> nodes)

      • toDot

        public static <D> java.lang.String toDot(java.lang.Iterable<? extends GraphUtils.TarjanNode<D>> nodes,
                                         java.lang.String name,
                                         java.lang.String header)
        Debugging: dot representation of a set of connected nodes. The resulting dot representation will use Node.toString to display node labels and Node.printDependency to display edge labels. The resulting representation is also customizable with a graph name and a header.
